{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glibobject\/bindingsignalname\/notify"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingSignalName"]]},"metadata":{"externalID":"s:10GLibObject17BindingSignalNameO6notifyyA2CmF","modules":[{"name":"GLibObject"}],"roleHeading":"Case","title":"BindingSignalName.notify","symbolKind":"case","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingSignalName\/notify"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"notify"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"explicitNotify","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"text":" results","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"If they did pass ","type":"text"},{"code":"explicitNotify","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", then this signal is emitted only","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify()"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"text":" call, like this:","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"syntax":"C","type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is important to note that you must use"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"#canonical-parameter-names"},{"text":" as","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"detail strings for the notify signal."}]}]}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set()"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject":{"abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","title":"GLibObject","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation